text: Eckwersheim is a commune. It is in Grand Est in the Bas-Rhin department in northeast France. It is about north of Strasbourg. On 14 November 2015, the a TGV train derailed while it was being tested along the LGV Est high-speed rail line. Eleven people were killed. == References == Category:Communes in Bas- Rhin
title: Eckwersheim
